---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover"/>
  <title>Pikanté — La michelada que prende todo</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Mix premium de michelada. Sirve, mezcla y disfruta. Hecho en México."/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ===== NAV ===== -->
<nav class="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo" aria-label="Pikante">
    <img src="/assets/lifestyle-pool.webp" alt="Pikante"/>
  </a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#sabores">Sabores</a>
    <a href="#preparar">Preparar</a>
    <a href="#vida">Vida Pikante</a>
    <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-cart">
    <span class="pill"><span class="dot"></span>Envio 24h</span>
    <!-- <span style="color:#cfcfcf">Carrito (0)</span> -->
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow-row">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <span>Mix de michelada &middot; Honduras</span>
        <span style="color:#3d3d3d">/</span>
        <span> Fuego en botella</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="h-display ">
        La <em class="flame-letter">Michelada</em><br/>
        Que <span class="stroke">Prende</span> Todo.
      </h1>
      <p class="sub">
        Intensa, fresca y con el balance perfecto entre sabor y fuego. Sirve, mezcla, y tu cerveza pasa de aburrida a iconica en 8 segundos.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#sabores">
          Comprar ahora
          <span class="arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#sabores">
          Ver sabores
          <span class="arrow">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div><b>4.9<span style="color:var(--accent)">/5</span></b><span>2,847 resenas</span></div>
        <div><b>8s</b><span>Sirve &middot; Mezcla &middot; Listo</span></div>
        <div><b>HN</b><span>Hecho en Honduras</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-photo reveal" style="transition-delay:.12s">
      <img src="/assets/hero-fire.webp" alt="Michelada Pikante con flamas"/>
      <span class="photo-tag">SKU-001 &middot; Original 320ml</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-corner">Scroll &middot; Encender</div>
</header>

<!-- ===== MARQUEE ===== -->
<div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <span>Mix de Michelada</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Hecho en Honduras</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span class="fire">100% Natural</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Sabor autentico</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Picante real</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Envio 24h</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Mix de Michelada</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Hecho en Honduras</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span class="fire">100% Natural</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Sabor autentico</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Picante real</span><span class="dot"></span>
    <span>Envio 24h</span><span class="dot"></span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ===== WHAT IS ===== -->
<section class="what">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">01 / Que es</span>
        <h2>Sirve. Mezcla.<br/><em>Prendela.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Pikante es el mix preparado que transforma cualquier cerveza en una michelada brutal. Sin sobres, sin licuadora, sin ciencia. Solo fuego en botella.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="what-list">
      <div class="what-item reveal">
        <span class="what-n">01</span>
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/>
            <path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h3>Sabor que se siente, no se explica.</h3>
          <p>Cuatro tipos de chile, jugo de limon real, especias de mercado y un toque secreto de tamarindo. Sin atajos.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="what-item reveal" style="transition-delay:.05s">
        <span class="what-n">02</span>
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M8 3h8l-1 4-2 13H11L9 7z"/>
            <path d="M10 9h4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h3>Picante perfecto.</h3>
          <p>Calibrado para que pique rico, no para que sufras. Tres niveles segun tu temperatura.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="what-item reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
        <span class="what-n">03</span>
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M13 2 4 14h6l-1 8 9-12h-6z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h3>Facil de preparar.</h3>
          <p>Escarcha el vaso, sirve cerveza, agrega Pikante. Listo. Hasta tu primo lo hace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="what-item reveal" style="transition-delay:.15s">
        <span class="what-n">04</span>
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M2 22l5-14 9 9z"/><path d="M14 4l2 2M18 2v3M21 7l-2 .5M14 11l3-3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h3>Ideal para fiestas.</h3>
          <p>Una botella alcanza para 8 micheladas. Llega, sirve y eres el heroe del rooftop.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="what-item reveal" style="transition-delay:.2s">
        <span class="what-n">05</span>
        <div class="what-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M20 4C10 4 4 10 4 20c10 0 16-6 16-16zM4 20l8-8"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="what-content">
          <h3>Ingredientes premium.</h3>
          <p>Colorantes naturales, especias reales. Lo que dice la etiqueta, lo que sabe el trago.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== HOW TO ===== -->
<section class="how" id="preparar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">02 / Como se prepara</span>
        <h2>Tres pasos.<br/><em>Cero pretexto.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Sin cocteleria de TikTok ni medidores raros. Ocho segundos del refri al primer trago.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <article class="step reveal">
        <div class="step-photo">
          <span class="num">01</span>
          <img src="/assets/product-limes.webp" alt="Escarchar el vaso con limon y chile"/>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <span class="mono">Paso 01</span>
          <h3>Escarcha el vaso</h3>
          <p>Limon en el borde, bano en chile en polvo. El ritual antes del fuego.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="step reveal" style="transition-delay:.08s">
        <div class="step-photo">
          <span class="num">02</span>
          <img src="/assets/prep-overhead.webp" alt="Agregar cerveza y Pikante"/>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <span class="mono">Paso 02</span>
          <h3>Cerveza + Pikante</h3>
          <p>2 partes de cerveza fria. 1 parte de Pikante. Hielo si la noche lo pide.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="step reveal" style="transition-delay:.16s">
        <div class="step-photo">
          <span class="num">03</span>
          <img src="/assets/hero-fire.webp" alt="Disfrutar la michelada Pikante"/>
        </div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <span class="mono">Paso 03</span>
          <h3>Disfruta el fuego</h3>
          <p>Brinda, prende la bocina, repite. Lo demas se cuenta solo.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PRODUCTS ===== -->
<section class="products" id="sabores">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">03 / Sabores</span>
        <h2>Elige tu<br/><em>temperatura.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Tres botellas. Tres formas de prender el rato. Todas hechas con la misma obsesion por el balance.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="prod-grid">
      <!-- Original -->
      <article class="prod reveal">
        <div class="prod-img">
          <span class="prod-tag hot">Mas vendido</span>
          <img src="/assets/product-limes.webp" alt="Pikante Original"/>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-body">
          <div class="prod-row1">
            <h3>Original</h3>
            <span class="price">L 129 <span style="color:#666">&middot; 320ml</span></span>
          </div>
          <p>El balance clasico: chile de arbol, limon, tamarindo. La puerta de entrada al fuego.</p>
          <div class="prod-row2">
            <span class="chiles" aria-label="Picante 3 de 5">
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
            </span>
            <button class="prod-cta">Agregar +</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Brutal -->
      <article class="prod reveal" style="transition-delay:.07s">
        <div class="prod-img">
          <span class="prod-tag">Edicion 02</span>
          <img src="/assets/hero-fire.webp" alt="Pikante Brutal"/>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-body">
          <div class="prod-row1">
            <h3>Brutal</h3>
            <span class="price">$149 <span style="color:#666">&middot; 320ml</span></span>
          </div>
          <p>Para los que no se andan con rodeos. Habanero ahumado, chile morita, jugo de naranja agria.</p>
          <div class="prod-row2">
            <span class="chiles" aria-label="Picante 5 de 5">
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
            </span>
            <button class="prod-cta">Agregar +</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Verde -->
      <article class="prod reveal" style="transition-delay:.14s">
        <div class="prod-img">
          <span class="prod-tag">Version suave</span>
          <img src="/assets/lifestyle-night.webp" alt="Pikante Verde"/>
        </div>
        <div class="prod-body">
          <div class="prod-row1">
            <h3>Verde</h3>
            <span class="price">L 129 <span style="color:#666">&middot; 320ml</span></span>
          </div>
          <p>Citrico, fresco, jalapeno verde y limon persa. La michelada de las 3pm en la alberca.</p>
          <div class="prod-row2">
            <span class="chiles" aria-label="Picante 2 de 5">
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile on"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
              <span class="chile"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2s-1.5 3-1.5 5 1.5 3 1.5 5-2 3-2 3 4-1 6-4 0-7 0-7-1 4-2 4 .5-4-2-6z"/><path d="M7 15c0-2 1-3 1-3s-3 1-3 4 3 5 3 5-1-2-1-3 0-3 0-3z"/></svg></span>
            </span>
            <button class="prod-cta">Agregar +</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== SOCIAL PROOF ===== -->
<section class="social">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">04 / Prueba social</span>
        <h2>No nos<br/><em>creas a nosotros.</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p>Cuatro mil setecientas resenas. La banda no miente cuando el trago esta bueno.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats reveal">
      <div class="stat"><b>+10K</b><span>Clientes felices</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b>+50K</b><span>Micheladas servidas</span></div>
      <div class="stat"><b><em>4.9</em>/5</b><span>Promedio &middot; 2,847 resenas</span></div>
